  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育系统设计一个核心的数据流架构。主要涉及成绩同步、课堂服务和LMS门户这几个模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那这几个模块之间的操作模式是怎样的？是标准的CRUD模式，还是有更复杂的构造逻辑？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CRUD",
        "Construction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两者都有。GradeSync负责创建和删除操作，ClassroomService主要做读取，LMS门户处理更新。同时还需要一个独立的Construction层来处理资源、设置和作业的构造。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create",
        "Delete",
        "Read",
        "Update",
        "constructResource",
        "constructSettings",
        "constructAssignment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出CRUD和Construction两个子图。GradeSync同时出现在Create和Delete节点中，ClassroomService对应Read，LMS门户对应Update。Construction层放三个构造器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CRUD",
        "Construction",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。另外还需要一个StateMapping层，专门处理远程状态、设置状态和作业状态的映射，都走ContentCDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "StateMapping",
        "mapRemoteState",
        "mapSettingsState",
        "mapAssignmentState",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "StateMapping子图已添加，三个映射节点都指向ContentCDN。接下来是Model层吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "StateMapping",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Model层有三个：ResourceModel和AssignmentModel放在StudentDB里，SettingsModel放在ContentCDN。",
