      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Read到三个StateMapping的连接。继续Construction到Model的连线：constructResource指向ResourceModel，constructSettings到SettingsModel，constructAssignment到AssignmentModel。",
      "elements_involved": [
