      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "StateMapping也要连到对应的Model。mapRemoteState和mapSettingsState分别对应ResourceModel和SettingsModel，mapAssignmentState对应AssignmentModel。",
